// are clipped when using Bootstrap's position:absolute. Use position:fixed aligned to the
// toggle's viewport rect and update on scroll (capture) / resize while open.
// Dropdown menus inside .gridcontainer.table-scroll-x pick up horizontal overflow and get
// clipped under Bootstrap's position:absolute. Use position:fixed aligned to the toggle's
// viewport rect and update on scroll (capture) / resize while open.
//
// Scoped to that wrapper only — applying fixed positioning for every clipped ancestor broke
